OL,3,CJersey Election 2026 live blog:
OL,4,CCounting underway after polls close
OL,6,FCounting is underway across Jersey as
OL,7,Fthe island elects its next set of
OL,8,Fpoliticians.
OL,10,FThe first results are expected within
OL,11,Fthe next couple of hours, with nine
OL,12,FSenators, 28 Deputies and 12
OL,13,FConstables seats to be filled for the
OL,14,Fnext four years.
OL,16,FITV Channel has reporters at counts
OL,17,Fthroughout the island and will bring
OL,18,Fyou all the results and reaction
OL,19,Fovernight.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
