OL,3,CJersey Election 2026 live blog:
OL,4,CCounting underway after polls close
OL,6,FFollow the live blog below and view
OL,7,Fthe full set of confirmed results so
OL,8,Ffar here.
OL,10,FThat's it! Jersey has chosen who it
OL,11,Fwants to be represented by for the
OL,12,Fnext four years. Now the counting
OL,13,Fbegins. Results for some seats are
OL,14,Fexpected to come in within the next
OL,15,Fcouple of hours, while some may take
OL,16,Fmuch longer. We're here for the long
OL,17,Fhaul, so check back throughout the
OL,18,Fnight as we bring you every result as
OL,19,Fit happens, plus all the reaction.
